T02TD2130E:176b-3: rtogs pa brjod pa sum cu pa //
T02TD2130E:176b-4: jo bo spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2130E:176b-5: rdo rje 'dzin pa tshangs dbang gtsug / chu skyes che dbus 'jig rten mgon //
T02TD2130E:176b-6: 'od zer rgyun gyis dbang bskur bas //
T02TD2130E:176b-7: ae ma dri gsum dag mdzad rmad //
T02TD2130E:176b-8: bstan pa'i lus ni ri bo 'dra //
T02TD2130E:176b-9: spros bral sems ni nam mkha' ste //
T02TD2130E:176b-10: g-yon pa'i sems ni rlung rgyun bcings //
T02TD2130E:176b-12: yid ni khyab 'jug nam mkha' ste //
T02TD2130E:176b-13: 'khor lo lnga yi rang bzhin lus //
T02TD2130E:176b-14: srog rtsol nyi ma zla ba gnyis //
T02TD2130E:176b-15: bde chen rdo rje'i zhags pas 'ching //
T02TD2130E:176b-16: dri ma lnga ni lnga yis spyong //
T02TD2130E:176b-17: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs //
T02TD2130E:176b-18: de dag ma bcos skye ba med //
T02TD2130E:176b-19: ae ma 'di ni bsgom bya gang //
T02TD2130E:176b-20: rgya mtsho'i snying po me 'bar bas //
T02TD2130E:176b-21: ri rab srog shing shing rta brgyud //
T02TD2130E:176b-22: tshangs dbang rtse nas char rgyun 'bab //
T02TD2130E:177a-2: gang ma rig pa de stong nyid //
T02TD2130E:177a-3: kun nas dkris pa bde ba'i tshal //
T02TD2130E:177a-5: lha mchog mi de gang gis bcings //
T02TD2130E:177a-6: lte ba'i mar mes mun pa bsal //
T02TD2130E:177a-7: snying gar shes rab padma rgyas //
T02TD2130E:177a-8: spyi gtsug ye shes bde chen 'dzag /
T02TD2130E:177a-9: da ni rang lus dngos grub 'gyur //
T02TD2130E:177a-11: bde chen dangs ma'i thig le gnas //
T02TD2130E:177a-12: de dbus rnam par mi rtog pa //
T02TD2130E:177a-13: ye shes mig gcig dri med nyid //
T02TD2130E:177a-15: nam mkha' la ni nyi shar bzhin //
T02TD2130E:177a-16: der yang mi gnas gzhan du'ang min //
T02TD2130E:177a-17: kye ho shin tu zab pa'i gnas //
T02TD2130E:177a-18: 'jig rten thams cad nam mkhas bcings //
T02TD2130E:177a-19: nam mkha' de yi sprin gyis bsgribs //
T02TD2130E:177a-20: gang tshe rtog pa'i sprin dag pa //
T02TD2130E:177a-21: de tshe 'di la ci zhig snang //
T02TD2130E:177a-22: sgyu mas sgyu ma'i grong khyer bcom //
T02TD2130E:177a-23: sems kyis sems ni slu ba ste //
T02TD2130E:177a-24: 'di nas bdag 'dras slu med rig / ae ma ho ae ma bla ma'i drin //
T02TD2130E:177a-26: bar ni rdo rje'i mdud pas bcings //
T02TD2130E:177a-27: steng du yi ge gyen du bsgyur //
T02TD2130E:177a-28: thabs ni bdag gis rang la rnyed //
T02TD2130E:177a-29: lus ni ri bo 'dra byas la //
T02TD2130E:177a-30: ngag ni rlung rgyun lta bur bsngams //
T02TD2130E:177a-31: sems ni nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
T02TD2130E:177a-32: dbyer med chos nyid kun gyi dngos //
T02TD2130E:177a-33: brtan lus shing rta rab bcas pa //
T02TD2130E:177a-34: g-yo ba srog shing lam du gzhug / de ltar bcings pa'i ting 'dzin ni //
T02TD2130E:177a-35: 'chi med nam mkha'i dngos grub thob //
T02TD2130E:177a-36: nam mkha'i rnal 'byor rnam mi rtog / yang dag lha ni bde ba che //
T02TD2130E:177a-38: gnas 'dir ngal ba so mkhas pa dag / rdo rje 'dzin pa rdo rje 'chang //
T02TD2130E:177a-39: rdo rje rgyal po rdo rje bde //
T02TD2130E:177a-40: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpas stong //
T02TD2130E:177a-41: ae ma rdo rje kun rig pa'o //
T02TD2130E:177a-42: me tog mthong gi rtsi mi mthong //
T02TD2130E:177a-43: chab rom mthong gi chu ma yin //
T02TD2130E:177a-44: lus mthong bde ba blang bar gyis //
T02TD2130E:177a-45: sems mthong mthong ba ma mchis so //
T02TD2130E:177a-46: chu nang skyes bus su yi bu //
T02TD2130E:177a-47: rmi lam grong khyer bdag po med //
T02TD2130E:177a-48: me long gzugs ni gang las 'ongs //
T02TD2130E:177a-50: gang na gnas dang skye ba dang //
T02TD2130E:177a-52: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid chos 'di la //
T02TD2130E:177a-53: kye ho 'jigs pa gang zhig yod //
T02TD2130E:177b-0: 'di dag @177b snang ba snang brnyan tsam //
T02TD2130E:177b-1: rig pa de yang rig pas dben //
T02TD2130E:177b-2: thams cad rig snyam shes snyam ste //
T02TD2130E:177b-3: tsam de la yang snyam nyid med //
T02TD2130E:177b-4: skyes bu don kun grub pa 'di //
T02TD2130E:177b-5: zhe sdang nyi ma 'od gsal lha //
T02TD2130E:177b-6: 'dod chags zla ba bde bas spyod //
T02TD2130E:177b-7: gti mug sgra gcan mi rtog 'joms //
T02TD2130E:177b-8: nam mkha'i sprin dang rgya mtsho'i rlabs //
T02TD2130E:177b-9: me tog rtsi dang ga bur dri //
T02TD2130E:177b-10: me long gzugs dang shel dkar bzhin //
T02TD2130E:177b-11: rnam rtog mi rtog dngos dbyer med //
T02TD2130E:177b-13: las ni nyon mongs de yi rgyu //
T02TD2130E:177b-14: mtshan ma yin te de shes nas //
T02TD2130E:177b-15: skyes bu mtshan med rnam par grol //
T02TD2130E:177b-16: rtog pa'i glang chen lcags kyus dgug //
T02TD2130E:177b-17: sems kyi bung ba rtsi yis bsdu //
T02TD2130E:177b-18: ting 'dzin dang po mtsho nang rtse //
T02TD2130E:177b-20: yid kyi mar mes mun pa sel //
T02TD2130E:177b-21: bde ba'i me tog bung bas 'jib //
T02TD2130E:177b-22: 'dzin pa'i rba rlab rgya mtshor thim //
T02TD2130E:177b-23: bde sdug sprin de nam mkhar dengs //
T02TD2130E:177b-24: yi ge gsum gyi brdas mtshon pas ;
T02TD2130E:177b-25: yi ge med pa bdag gis rtogs //
T02TD2130E:177b-26: rnal 'byor rgyal po yi ge mchog / sems la gzhan ni ma mchis so //
T02TD2130E:177b-28: gnas zhes bya bar ga la 'gyur //
T02TD2130E:177b-29: gang mi gnas pa chos kyi dbyings //
T02TD2130E:177b-31: rtag tu byed bral gti mug med //
T02TD2130E:177b-32: khro khro bag chags gtan bcom pa //
T02TD2130E:177b-33: zhi ba'i dam pa mya ngan 'das //
T02TD2130E:177b-34: gter chen rang la yod shes kyis //
T02TD2130E:177b-35: 'jig rten sgyu ma'i las kyis bsgrubs //
T02TD2130E:177b-36: sgyu ma sgyu ma'i yid kyis te //
T02TD2130E:177b-37: 'di kun sgyu ma nyid shes na //
T02TD2130E:177b-38: sgyu ma lta bur rnam par grol //
T02TD2130E:177b-39: sgyu mar rtogs pas bden rtog 'joms //
T02TD2130E:177b-40: rtog med sgyu ma la mi gnas //
T02TD2130E:177b-41: mi gnas 'gro la phan brtson pas //
T02TD2130E:177b-42: ae ma nor bu rin chen rnyed /
T02TD2130E:177b-43: rtogs pa brjod pa sum cu pa zhes bya ba rdzogs so /
T02TD2130E:177b-45: // / rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po mi tra dzo kyi de nyid kyi spyan sngar //
T02TD2130E:177b-46: gnubs lo ts'a ba byams pa'i dpal gyis bsgyur ba'o /
